            , were indicted for <rs id="t18021027-83-off456" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18021027-83-off456" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18021027-83-off456" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18021027-83-cd457" type="crimeDate">8th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-83-off456 t18021027-83-cd457"></join>, a hat, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18021027-83-victim757" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Clements
                  <interp inst="t18021027-83-victim757" type="surname" value="Clements"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18021027-83-victim757" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
